app_description: Translate between any of 100 languages while online. We also provide you with VPN functionality to enhance translation speed. Take a photo of a menu road sign book page or choose a photo with text from your camera roll to see its translation over the image only available when you re online . Visual text recognition is currently available in 45 languages: Czech English French German Italian Polish Portuguese Russian Spanish Turkish Chinese Ukrainian and more Provide fast and secure VPN proxy service. Quick check: just enter a few letters and start translating. Zero cost: the DeepL translation app is completely free. Camera translation: point your camera at the text in the image and get an instant translation. Image translation: import images for high quality translation.
